node.text: I’m delighted to be joining the @antrimcoasthalfmarathon this year. Unfortunately, I won’t be running but I will be getting involved. I enjoyed it last year. So much scenery, lovely people.  This year I’m going to be behind it and get involved with the Kid’s race … so don’t miss out and I’ll see you there.  #EmbraceAGiantSpirit, @CoastHalf, @NITouristBoard, @mea_bc, @NIElectricity, @LanyonGroup, @SPARintheUK @discoverni
